prevention of natural disasters, and the mitigation of their consequences. Several 
respondents felt that there should be a greater focus on ex ante disaster prevention, risk 
reduction, emergency preparedness and improved and sustainable rehabilitation. Greater 
predictability of assistance and increased funds for the United Nations emergency relief 
coordination are desirable. Adequate investment is required firstly to reduce vulnerability to </footnote>0-14914 
