 I.M. Young, &#8220;Responsibility and global justice: a social connection model&#8221;, 2006, 23 (1) <i>Social 
</i></p>
<p><i>Philosophy and Policy</i>, p. 102; O. O&#8217;Neill, <i>The Bounds of Justice</i>, Cambridge University Press, New 
York, 2000. 
</p>
<p> 
